name: Two Souls
description:
I wanted to create a visual representation of extroversion vs introversion. An open hand can conjure a feeling of trust. The woman in front looks directly into the eyes of the viewer, with and open and relaxed hand. More hidden, the other faces away with closed eyes. One’s energy is internally directed, while the other’s is externally projected to the outside world.

(3507x5262)

Type: Gif
